A package manager for Minigrace.

grace-pkg build [pkg]

  Builds a package. With no arguments, builds the package in the current
  directory. Given a URL, retrieves the package at that URL and build it.

grace-pkg install [--global] [pkg]

  Installs a package into the local package repository. With no arguments,
  installs the package in the current directory. Given a URL, retrieves the
  package at that URL and installs it.

grace-pkg bundle [--static]

  Bundles up the current directory into a tarball. The static flag will include
  all dependencies in the bundle.

